WEBVTT

00:07:27.214 --> 00:07:30.191
the confusion that I felt,

00:07:30.191 --> 00:07:34.993
because now I realized that 
what was done to me was a terrible thing

00:07:34.993 --> 00:07:37.977
that in this society was called barbaric,

00:07:37.977 --> 00:07:39.944
it was called mutilation.

00:07:39.944 --> 00:07:42.107
My mother had said
it was called circumcision,

00:07:42.107 --> 00:07:44.327
but here it was mutilation.

00:07:44.327 --> 00:07:47.384
I was thinking, I'm mutilated?
I'm a mutilated person.

00:07:47.384 --> 00:07:49.114
Oh my God.

00:07:49.114 --> 00:07:51.002
And then the anger came.

00:07:51.002 --> 00:07:55.002
I was a black angry woman.
(Laughter)

00:07:55.002 --> 00:07:56.379
Oh yeah.

00:07:56.379 --> 00:07:58.864
A little one, but angry nevertheless.

00:07:59.994 --> 00:08:03.720
I went home and said to my mom,